Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.bag.mutable.primitive

Class FloatHashBag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.collections.impl.primitive.AbstractFloatIterable
      • org.eclipse.collections.impl.bag.mutable.primitive.FloatHashBag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, FloatBag, MutableFloatBag, MutableFloatCollection, FloatIterable, PrimitiveIterable

    public final class FloatHashBag
extends AbstractFloatIterable
implements MutableFloatBag, java.io.Externalizable
    FloatHashBag is similar to HashBag, and is memory-optimized for float primitives. This file was automatically generated from template file primitiveHashBag.stg.
    Since:
    3.0.
